text:
Squatters Colony: Manhattan: Three views of itinerants occupying the cleared area on the South side of W. Houston Street, between Mercer and Greene Streets. This site is a portion of the 100 foot swath that Eighth Avenue subway construction necessitated.

About 1935
Views: 1-2-3

Gift of Committee on Housing
Charity Organization Society
